ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations
PrecisRegulations amending the IMMIGRATION AND REFUGEE PROTECTION REGULATIONS in order to help support the Government's response to COVID-19 pandemic to implement any decision to restrict entry into Canada and to ensure the ongoing integrity of our borders in the economic interests of Canada and the health and safety of Canadians.
